snippet.title: Helldivers 2 - Co-op and Combat Trailer | PS5 & PC Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/helldivers-2/

Stratagems return with bigger and badder weapons and gear than ever before. Find out how teaming up with friends may make or break your mission in HELLDIVERS 2.

Join the Helldivers to fight for freedom across a hostile galaxy in third-person co-op shooter operations. Developed by Arrowhead Game Studios. Coming soon to PlayStation 5 and Steam on PC.

Internet connection required. Paid PS Plus subscription required to play on PS5; fees recur until cancelled. Age restrictions apply. Full terms: play.st/psplus-usageterms

May contain content inappropriate for children. Visit http://www.esrb.org for rating information.
